Description: VibeOS desktop branding and Pacific Dawn theme
 Ships the VibeOS Pacific Dawn KDE Look-and-Feel package, matching
 color scheme, wallpaper set, Plymouth splash, SDDM theming config,
 Orbitron + JetBrains Mono fonts, and the /etc/os-release branding.
 .
 After install the Look-and-Feel theme is applied system-wide and
 Plymouth is switched to the vibeos-pacific-dawn boot splash.
